        <h2>
            狗日的战争2的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7380651">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7380651/" class="title-link">三条线的叙述方式，从2开始感觉有点别扭</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7380651"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/71264896/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u71264896-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/71264896/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">wuyve</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-02-15"
      class="main-meta">2015-02-15 20:28:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7380651_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读完了1之后迫不及待的买了2和3的电子版，一天半的时间读完了 虽然在1里的叙事也是三线展开，但在2里有点不适应了。可能是因为1中翠儿线和解放战争线只是老旦抗日线的插叙，但到了2和3里三条线已经并驾齐驱、有点不分主次的缘故吧 不过仅仅是稍微的不适，不影响对4的大结局的期待

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7380651_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7380651_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










